00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:26.720
Frankly, because I wasn't a big fan of Java.

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:29.120
And I got tired of developing in Java.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.260
So I gave up on that.

00:05:30.260 --> 00:05:34.940
But when I had this exposure to Python, it was such an easy language to get into.

00:05:34.940 --> 00:05:37.980
The syntax was really kind of readable.

00:05:37.980 --> 00:05:40.060
I didn't need to be a software developer.

00:05:40.060 --> 00:05:42.940
I could kind of dabble with it for a little bit and then come back.

00:05:42.980 --> 00:05:44.540
