I think also like sysadmins probably had a similar experience as well.

00:23:23.040 --> 00:23:32.320
I've seen it in the same, I mean, the installation, I think the farther you get from the end product, and the end product for most of these cases is some piece of software someplace.

00:23:33.100 --> 00:23:38.860
And so the farther you are from the end product, the longer it took for some of this pressure to kind of go through.

